OL,3,C'Worrying times' as award-winning
OL,4,Cfoodbank announces closure
OL,6,FITV News' Kathy Wardle spoke to those
OL,7,Fin charge at Newquay's Drop In and
OL,8,FShare Centre.
OL,10,FA food bank and support centre in
OL,11,FCornwall will close due to a shortage
OL,12,Fof funding - with those in charge
OL,13,F"incredibly worried" about support for
OL,14,Flocal families in its absence.
OL,16,FNewquay's Drop In and Share Centre
OL,17,F(DISC) has given out one million free
OL,18,Fmeals over the last seven years and
OL,19,Fwas given a King's Award for Voluntary
OL,20,FService in 2023.
