OL,3,C'Worrying times' as award-winning
OL,4,Cfoodbank announces closure
OL,6,FHowever, the centre will close on the
OL,7,F1 January 2025, following a final
OL,8,FChristmas toy and food giveaway.
OL,10,FMonique Collins, who has run the
OL,11,Fcentre for seven years told ITV News
OL,12,FWest Country that she had "no other
OL,13,Fchoice" saying: "When I made the
OL,14,Fdecision, it wasn't an easy one to
OL,15,Fmake, it was a very difficult decision.
OL,17,F"There is no funding for grassroots
OL,18,Forganisations like ourselves. Everyone
OL,19,Fsignposts to us, and the demand has
OL,20,Fjust outgrown what we can offer."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
