OL,3,C'Worrying times' as award-winning
OL,4,Cfoodbank announces closure
OL,6,FMonique has said she has already had
OL,7,Fto cut back the number of meals given
OL,8,Fout each week despite having 3000
OL,9,Fpeople registered for help.
OL,11,F"I'm incredibly worried especially
OL,12,Fwhen I look at the demand we've
OL,13,Falready got coming in for Christmas
OL,14,Fpresents. There are so many families
OL,15,Fstruggling with toys, with food, with
OL,16,Fgas, with electric - it's like a
OL,17,Fgaping hole and it's not being filled.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
