OL,3,C'Worrying times' as award-winning
OL,4,Cfoodbank announces closure
OL,6,F"It's very worrying times for
OL,7,FNewquay... I don't know what the
OL,8,Ffuture holds... I'm glad that I could
OL,9,Fjust make a slight bit of difference
OL,10,Fto people's lives and that's what I'm
OL,11,Fgrateful for."
OL,13,FCarol Boyle, who works at DISC, said
OL,14,Fshe was also worried about how local
OL,15,Ffamilies would be supported when the
OL,16,Fcharity closes: "We get homeless
OL,17,Fpeople, people that have nothing -
OL,18,Fjust living in a bus shelter so they
OL,19,Fcome in we obviously feed them, we've
OL,20,Fgot young families fleeing domestic
OL,21,Fviolence.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
